  "notes": "NCSC-CAF-ONT provides a comprehensive model of the UK Cyber Assessment Framework v4.0 for AI-agent-driven compliance assessment. The ontology enables automated CAF assessment workflows, sector-specific CAF Profile targeting, gap analysis with remediation prioritisation, and cross-framework compliance mapping to MCSB (Azure cloud controls), RMF-IS27005 (ISO 27005 risk management), and GRC-FW (organisational compliance posture). Source data derived from Erreinion/NCSC_CAF_v4 structured IGP dataset."
